Package com.example.survivorbuddy4mobile

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BuddyAudioActivity
    The control screen for incoming audio server of SurvivorBuddy
    BuddyAudioServer
    A TCP server which receives data from client and writes it to a PipedOutputStream
    BuddyAudioService
    BuddyAudioService controls BuddyAudioServer and runs in the background continually until explicitly stopped in BuddyAudioActvity
    BuddyMessageServer
    A TCP server which receives packets of text encoded as UTF-8 and writes it to an PipedOutputStream
    BuddyMessageService
    A service controlled by MessageActivity.
    ExampleInstrumentedTest
    Instrumented test, which will execute on an Android device.
    MainActivity
    The main screen of the application.
    MessageActivity
    The activity which displays messages received from the PC SurvivorBuddy app Starts a Service which starts a TCP server
    RtspService
    A service which controls a RtspServer for sending Camera and Mic audio
    SettingsActivity
    Activity used to change the port settings for BuddyMessageServer, BuddyAudioServer, and RtspServer Also displays the current IP address of the device
    TestBuddyAudioServer
    Set of unit tests for BuddyAudioServer
    TestBuddyMessageServer
    Set of unit tests for BuddyMessageServer
    Utils
    Externally found set of utilities.
